A high-angle macro photograph of the front visor viewport section of a carbon-fiber flight helmet prototype. A flat Project ARMO-88 dielectric metalens plate is being securely locked down inside an internal step-flange seating shelf via twin recessed metal tension clips. The glass-smooth quartz lens plate catches sharp purplish anti-reflective cross-lighting, showing a sub-wavelength nano-pillar array etched inside. Handheld technical tools and micro-gaskets lie scattered on an orange workshop matting bench, cleanroom prototype assembly focus, crisp details --ar 16:9
